14 WHEREAS, the organization was named Small Business of the Year in 2024 by Douglas
15 County in recognition of its outstanding contributions to the local economy and its role as
16 a model of excellence in senior services; and
17 WHEREAS, Serenity Empire Senior Living remains steadfast in its mission to create a
18 nurturing and safe environment for seniors during their golden years, continually raising the
19 standard for person-centered care; and
20 WHEREAS, through its dedication and innovation, Serenity Empire Senior Living serves as
21 an inspiring example of excellence for providers throughout Georgia and beyond, making
22 it abundantly fitting and proper that it be appropriately honored.
23 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
24 recognize and commend Serenity Empire Senior Living for its commitment to senior
25 well-being, community development, and outstanding leadership in the field of elder care as
26 well as extend best wishes for continued success.
27 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
28 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Serenity Empire
29 Senior Living.
